  "strategy": [
    "Always handle all uncontrollable events in every state to ensure robustness.",
    "Use commit states to enforce consistent action execution and prevent oscillations.",
    "After obstacle detection, require a recovery/escape action before resuming forward movement.",
    "Prioritize blue object acquisition by transitioning to move_to_blue_commit upon blue_seen.",
    "Allow stop as a controllable action only in blue-seen-related states.",
